FestivalPlanner.GUI.AgendaGUI.PopUpGUI

Class AboutPopUp

  • java.lang.Object
    • FestivalPlanner.GUI.AbstractGUI
      • FestivalPlanner.GUI.AgendaGUI.PopUpGUI.AbstractCreationPopUp
        • FestivalPlanner.GUI.AgendaGUI.PopUpGUI.AboutPopUp

  • public class AboutPopUp
extends AbstractCreationPopUp
    Contains everything related to the AboutPopUp you get when clicking the About option in the MenuBar of the AgendaModule.

    The PopUp contains 3 text Nodes and a Button. The text elements show:

    • The software's author.
    • The author's motto.
    • The software's version.
